title: Kickoff time, broadcast set for Arkansas at Ole Miss game on Nov. 7
text:
Kickoff time, broadcast set for Arkansas at Ole Miss game on Nov. 7 THE ASSOCIATED PRESS First Posted: October 26, 2015 - 3:21 pmLast Updated: October 26, 2015 - 3:21 pm We also have more stories about: (click the phrases to see a list) 
Organizations: 
Arkansas (508) 
FAYETTEVILLE, Arkansas â€” Kickoff time and broadcast information are set for the Arkansas at Ole Miss football game on Nov. 7. 
Arkansas officials announced Monday that the game in Oxford, Mississippi, will start at 2:30 p.m. and be broadcast on CBS. 
The Razorbacks have won three of the last five games against Ole Miss and hold a 33-27-1 all-time record against the Rebels.
